==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Iron-sick
<hw>I"ron-sick`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>
<def>Having the ironwork loose or corroded; -- said of a ship when her
bolts and nails are so eaten with rust that she has become
leaky.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>iron sickness</ent>⟦br⟧
